}

q {
Q:"Two matrices A and B are conformable for the product AB if:"
A:"d"
O:a) "Both A and B are square", b) "Both A and B are symmetric", c) "Number of rows of A = number of columns of B", d) "Number of columns of A = number of rows of B"
