}

q {
Q:"The transpose of a column matrix is a:"
A:"d"
O:a) "Zero matrix", b) "Diagonal matrix", c) "Column matrix", d) "Row matrix"
R:"Transposing swaps dimensions: \\(n \\times 1\\) becomes \\(1 \\times n\\), which is a row matrix."
}

q {
Q:"The transpose of a zero matrix is a:"
A:"b"
O:a) "Column matrix", b) "Zero matrix", c) "Row matrix", d) "Scalar matrix"
R:"Swapping rows and columns of a zero matrix leaves it unchanged."
}

q {
Q:"Roots of the equation \\(x^2 - 7x + 10 = 0\\) are:"
A:"c"
O:a) "\\(\\{2, -5\\}\\)", b) "\\(\\{-2, 5\\}\\)", c) "\\(\\{2, 5\\}\\)", d) "\\(\\{-2, -5\\}\\)"
